Other     Horizontal lists  A horizontal list is just a grid with only one row. Here's an example horizontal list (grid) of emails:    abacon52@time.com abiasini11@stanford.edu agarett6e@unblog.fr agwilt1e@sitemeter.com ajekel58@unblog.fr anewbigging5f@prnewswire.com apeters7j@amazon.com      Here's what the configuration for the grid above looks like:    import   {   Grid   }   from   "react-window" ;   

 function   HorizontalList ( {   emails   } :   {   emails :   string [ ]   } )   {   
